title: Whitney Port Is Pregnant! See Her Bare-Bellied Announcement!
text:
Congrats, gurl!
Whitney Port may be done with The Hills , but she's just getting started with The Bumps !
Just a month after her former costar Lauren Conrad announced her own baby news , the MTV star announced on Thursday that she's pregnant with her first child with husband Tim Rosenman !
Photos: The Hills Cast: Where Are They Now? 
Taking a page from Beyonce 's book and sharing a pic of her bare belly (above), writing:
"Oh hey! Just standing by the window in my underwear, with a BABY in my belly!!!"
